Subject: DoS in Microsoft Windows Live Messenger <= 8.0

Any one can make a DOS in the Microsoft Windows Live Messenger <= 8.0.

Steps:
1. go to tools
2. optinos
3. messages
4. uncheck the gestual emoticons

